<Content>cant go wrong with this hotel slap bang in the gay area of berlin it has a mixed clientel. ive stayed here on many occasion. most rooms have now been refurbished to a good standard. they say you get what you pay for but with this place you cant go wrong. the newer rooms are light and airy, some with private bathrooms, pay less and you share a bathroom on the landings. its centrally located with a 2 minute walk to nollendorfplatz station. i cantcomment on the breakfast because ive never been awake at that time to try it.id happily recommend this place to anyone. 
